<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p>My Club was born from a need to manage volunteer clubs and organizations, specifically those associated with Rotary International.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col col-md-12">
        <p>My Club is organized around three key entity types.  They are Districts, Clubs, and Members.  A District is a collection of Clubs, which is itself a collection of Members.  While there are additional layers of organizational heirarchy (Area, Regions, etc.), the scope of 'My Club' is limited ot Districts, Clubs, and Members.</p>
    </div>
</div>


<hr>

