                    <i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i> Clubs</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-center">

                </div>
                <p>Clubs are collections of members that operate with their own charter. Clubs typically have a meeting schedule, a calendar of events, and a collection of projects performed by Members.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="row justify-content-md-center">


